But when asked if he plans on requesting more players in January, he said: &quot;I don&rsquo;t want to speak about this. We have just started December and there is one month until January, then about this topic I think it is better to speak to the club and to tell my opinion. <br />
<br />
&quot;Then, like every time, the last decision was the club. I can give my opinion but the last decision is of the club, and it is right to do this.&quot;
